\p 
\v 1 Kitah kot…ôhrun m…ôm…ô nian r…ôfin Uhg…®n tat…®t…ôp…®n suah k…ôti k…ôni m…ôt…ôf…ôri in m…ôm…ô otuva pris asoli ag…®n, m…ôm…ô in suaru r…ôha n…ôt…ômimi ok…ôhuv…ôn o Uhg…®n. In suaru r…ôhalah o n…ôf…ôni…ôn natimnati k…ôm Uhg…®n, k…ôni in matol sakrifais o r…ôhalah noli…ôn t…ôrah m…®n.\f + \fr 5:1 \ft Hip 2:17; 7:27; 8:3; 9:9\f*
