\q1 ‚ÄúIk pris k…ôti t…ôhmen e Melkis…®tek aup…ôn,\f + \fr 5:6 \ft Jen 14:18-20; Sek 6:13; Hip 5:10; 6:20; 7:1-22\f*\f + \fr 5:6 \ft Melkis…®tek (Jen 14:18) in kig r…ôha Salem (Salem u, n…®p…ôt…®n u, N…ôm…ôlinui…ôn) k…ôni in pris r…ôha Uhg…®n Il…®s P…®k. In t…ôm…ôtat…®g e nian r…ôha Epraham. Kr…®sto in t…ôhmen e Melkis…®tek m…ôt…ôu-inu in pris m…®ne in kig m…®n. M…ôt…ôu n…ôuan…®l…ôu…®s r…ôha Eron m…®n, ilah pris m…®n …ôm…ô, m…ôt…ôu s…ôni…ôm…ô kig m…®n; K…ôni Melkis…®tek in pris itul…®n i…ôt…ôm Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôf…ôri aup…ôn ag…®n, u…ôris…®g t…ôf…ôri Eron. Hip 7:2.\f*
