\v 7 E n…ômi…ôg…ôhi…ôn r…ôha Kr…®sto e n…ôhue n…®ft…ôni u, in t…ôt…ôfaki k…ôm Uhg…®n, m…ôt…ôtapu…ôh o nasirui…ôn, m…ôtas…ôk …ôf…ôm…ôh, n…ôhu n…ôhmt…®n t…ôtai…ôh. Uhg…®n tatos n…ôsan…ôni…ôn o nosmi…ôg…ôhi…ôn in e n…®m…®si…ôn. K…ôni in t…ômat…®siai Uhg…®n, k…ôni matol n…ôuian,\f + \fr 5:7 \ft Luk 22:42\f* k…ôni o nati u, Uhg…®n t…ôm…ôt…ôu in.\f + \fr 5:7 \ft Mat 26:36-46; Mak 14:32-42; Luk 22:39-46\f*
