\v 4 m…ôt…ôu-inu n…®ra n…ôni m…®ne kau in t…ôruru ag…®n nos r…ôk…®si…ôn t…ôfag…ô t…ôrah.\f + \fr 10:4 \ft Hip 9:12-14\f*
