\v 9 K…ôni u…ôris…®g, Kr…®sto t…ôt…ôni m…®n m…ôm…ô, ‚ÄúI…ôu u, i…ômuva m…ôm…ô i…ôkol n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn r…ôham.‚Äù E n…ôghati…ôn u r…ôhan, in tatoh r…ôk…®s n…ôni…ôskas…®ki…ôn …ôuas r…ôha nasirui…ôn, m…ôm…ô in ot…ôl…ôhu n…ôni…ôskas…®ki…ôn vi r…ôha nasirui…ôn k…ôti.
\v 10 K…ôni Iesu Kr…®sto t…ômol n…ôt…ôl…®gi…ôn r…ôha Uhg…®n tol lanu. In t…ômol sakrifais aru e n…®p…ôt…®n,\f + \fr 10:10 \ft Hip 2:14\f* mau k…ôti…ôh …ôm…ô,\f + \fr 10:10 \ft Hip 7:27\f* m…ôm…ô otol kitah kotasim, kitah u r…ôhan m…®n n…ôt…ômimi.\f + \fr 10:10 \ft Hip 10:14; Ef…ôs 5:26\f*
